<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0063a" xml:id="I01.0025.0063a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0063a01"/><cb:docNumber>No. 25</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0063a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>常煥等造浮圖記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb n="0064a" xml:id="I01.0025.0064a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0064a01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0064a0101">夫守真者淨。淨為悟法之基。培本者因因即現
<lb ed="I" n="0064a02"/>果之證。西域之聖靈宣布。而東土之妙諦迺得
<lb ed="I" n="0064a03"/>矣。方大化之初流。遐<note n="0064001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31174"/>＝陬【史】</note><note n="0064001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31174"/>【佛拓】，陬【史】</note><app n="0064001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">陬</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB31174"/></rdg></app>咸被其光。洎金象之呈
<lb ed="I" n="0064a04"/>露。智愚胥仰其暉。是以豪眉之容。飾于陽門。紺
<lb ed="I" n="0064a05"/>髮之形。圖諸夜臺。逮　　皇魏受圖。光宅崧洛。
<lb ed="I" n="0064a06"/>篤信彌殷。法教愈盛。王公貴人。舍眥財如脫屣。
<lb ed="I" n="0064a07"/>樵<note n="0064002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31175"/>＝豎【史】</note><note n="0064002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31175"/>【佛拓】，豎【史】</note><app n="0064002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">豎</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB31175"/></rdg></app>牧奴。視服役如<note n="0064003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30501"/>＝歸【史】</note><note n="0064003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30501"/>【佛拓】，歸【史】</note><app n="0064003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">歸</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30501"/></rdg></app>市。于是招提森列。寶塔
<lb ed="I" n="0064a08"/>高聳。金剎耀日。宮殿暎月。寫天上之姿。模山中
<lb ed="I" n="0064a09"/>之影。袈衣未啟。士女之羅拜滿前。經<note n="0064004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">声＝聲【史】</note><note n="0064004" resp="ihp" type="mod">声【佛拓】，聲【史】</note><app n="0064004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">聲</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">声</rdg></app>迭續。檀
<lb ed="I" n="0064a10"/>越之<note n="0064005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB10782"/>＝參【史】</note><note n="0064005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB10782"/>【佛拓】，參【史】</note><app n="0064005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">參</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB10782"/></rdg></app>贊盈階。粉飾<note n="0064006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB00982"/>＝莊【史】</note><note n="0064006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB00982"/>【佛拓】，莊【史】</note><app n="0064006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">莊</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB00982"/></rdg></app>嚴。莫令為逾。佛弟子常
<lb ed="I" n="0064a11"/>煥等。以寺內有五級浮圖一塸。建自永昌。後因
<lb ed="I" n="0064a12"/>兵劫。遂至巔仆。雖屢加增葺。絕少完<note n="0064007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30502"/>＝繕【史】</note><note n="0064007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30502"/>【佛拓】，繕【史】</note><app n="0064007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">繕</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30502"/></rdg></app>。今集眾
<lb ed="I" n="0064a13"/>同建。庶臻永固。非敢云不可稱量。不可思議之
<lb ed="I" n="0064a14"/>功德。<note n="0064008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30503"/>＝直【史】</note><note n="0064008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30503"/>【佛拓】，直【史】</note><app n="0064008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">直</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30503"/></rdg></app>願恒河沙數。同追斯福。
<lb ed="I" n="0064a15"/>　　大魏孝昌二年歲次丙午八月庚辰朔四
<lb ed="I" n="0064a16"/>　　日癸未建訖
<lb ed="I" n="0064a17"/>　　鎮遠將軍洛州騎兵<app type="star" corresp="#0064005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">參</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB10782"/></rdg></app>軍常煥
<lb ed="I" n="0064a18"/>　　冠軍將軍并州刺史杜延
<lb ed="I" n="0064a19"/>　　浮圖主修梵寺法師曇印
<lb ed="I" n="0064a20"/>　　浮圖主胡統寺法師道顯
<lb ed="I" n="0064a21"/>　　浮圖主景明寺法師雲淨
<lb ed="I" n="0064a22"/>　　浮圖主<note n="0064009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30505"/>＝莊【史】</note><note n="0064009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30505"/>【佛拓】，莊【史】</note><app n="0064009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">莊</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30505"/></rdg></app>嚴寺法師法悟
<lb ed="I" n="0064a23"/>　　唯那主　譚庚　　常印　　栢年
<lb ed="I" n="0064a24"/>　　唯那主　劉遷　　邊紹　　江尚
<lb ed="I" n="0064a25"/>　　唯那主　古啟　　祖任</p></cb:div>
